{"tid":2297224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国成立「武則天她媽在欽州」歷史文化研究組","createTime":"2020-11-23T06:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T06:44:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bea22384ea13dd478f3772c51e9737103fb99b29","tid":2297224,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"上游新聞報導，靈山縣文化廣電體育旅遊局副局長、「武則天她媽在欽州」歷史文化研究工作組辦公室主任勞德聯表示，這份文件屬實，並稱命名之前，工作組成員也曾討論過該命名會引發熱議，「但武則天她媽就是她媽，我們選擇用客觀事實直白表述，網友、各界人士熱議也沒關係」。<br />\n<br />\n靈山縣位於廣西南部，欽州市的中部。11月19日「通知」稱，為進一步推動「武則天她媽在欽州」歷史文化研究，挖掘靈山歷史文化遺產，豐富靈山歷史文化底蘊，保護和傳承靈山歷史文化，經縣人民政府同意，決定成立「武則天她媽在欽州」歷史文化研究工作組。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，靈山縣文化廣電體育旅遊局官方微信公眾號「靈山文旅」十月間兩次推送武則天與靈山的故事，詳述武則天其母楊氏於隋朝大業六年出生於欽州靈山縣武利鎮，後被欽州寧氏家族收養，後楊氏隨寧長真遷至長安。<br />\n<br />\n楊氏被武士彠納為小妾後，生下三個女兒，次女名武曌，小名媚娘，也就是日後的武則天。<br />\n<br />\n勞德聯表示，這些歷史事實在「永樂大典」和「四庫全書」都有記載，並非空穴來風。靈山縣早在上世紀50年代已開始關注武則天其母楊氏經歷，但是沒有認真進行資料搜集。他說，目前工作組對史料的搜集工作正在進行，同時也對已搜集到的一些口述、文字等材料進行真實性甄別、考證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/19/realtime/9105938.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F19%2Frealtime%2F9105938.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=a09dbc65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7333/5028857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7333%2F5028857&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=260c0c6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7333/5028857</a>"},{"pid":"8c1ed50cda6dfd6f818a41520adfd741973d3738","tid":2297224,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8127ed415e1c8266419cf66b37c92a60df72396","tid":2297224,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3f2ccc2432c21f808e117cb9ce74c44fdce67e","tid":2297224,"uid":45376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"所以話細個啲中文教畜死都要話支那話=好嘅中文鼓勵去學都痴撚線<br />\n屌你老母命個名都咁撚核突"},{"pid":"88f76e2665b8a27d9a6512018c8ee2d1ca17adf8","tid":2297224,"uid":65686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"相知班官開會嘅過程係點"},{"pid":"f928f75e92d77483f7c2e716404cc4aeaa68defd","tid":2297224,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"她媽的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d959be9cc3fe8aa5a426f601328112c6bde516","tid":2297224,"uid":380779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"冇文化嘅生番係咁上下"},{"pid":"2bab96e0735b6ff10214c144710305c5c21a3450","tid":2297224,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"成個中土古代幾千年文明真係完全糟蹋哂<br />\n<br />\n好中意睇唐宋明代既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa68d7d4b7025fa4d11800c1838106533bb78c6","tid":2297224,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"幾有趣"},{"pid":"9ba970779ec9621d0553bbe8d2dff2657850ded1","tid":2297224,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cla